===Etymology===
[[spy]] + [[ware]] as [[software]]

===Noun===
'''spyware'''
#a program that monitors the actions of a computer, and transmits transmits this data via the Internet. Spyware is distributed by being bundled with programs that users are likely to download, and it is then installed without the user knowing. The term spyware overlaps with [[adware]], although spyware is considered to be more unethical.

